HOME_PAGE\New.html. 
There was a bug in the Windows 2.4 version. 
Amaya generated always a \ even if the URI was a Web address. 
Help If you call InitDocView (CurrentDocument, ....) instead of InitDocView (0, in the function InitializeNewDoc, it should display the new document in the same window. 
Irene. 
