New.html comes from the global variable DocumentName. 
This variable is intialized in Amaya\amaya\init.c and you can change its intial value by whatever you want. 
I'm not sure that I understood well your question but you may have a new window if you asked for or if the current document is modified. 
Otherwise and exept for Help, new docs are displyed in the same window. 
